{"tid":827631,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［狗奴才] 點先train到我隻狗定點去廁所？","createTime":"2018-09-19T05:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T06:25:27.000Z","uid":88914,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a0d87cbda1454f5f93aba312426bd02f5257ed36","tid":827631,"uid":88914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T05:19:07.000Z","msg":"狗女1歲幾 仲未識得定點去廁所<br />\n屋企係木地板 佢一尿尿就好麻煩<br />\n佢一日會去兩次 早晚各一次<br />\n每次佢屙既時候都係我同屋企人望唔到既時候<br />\n例子：本身我同佢係廳 我入房拎少少嘢 之後就發現佢係廳已經屙左 <br />\n佢屙嚟屙去都係廳中間 我試過擺尿布係廳中間 <br />\n但佢唔屙 最後趁我入廚房飲水個時係無尿布既位置屙左<br />\n<br />\n而家試緊困住佢係一個地方 然後等佢屙<br />\n但今朝11點困到而家 同佢講要尿尿同屎屎先有得去玩<br />\n佢仲未有反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好唔忍心繼續困<br />\n佢係個地方到又好慘咁叫 好似叫我放佢咁<br />\n有無咩辦法教到佢隻蠢豬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd114ae7e8e323a7d13439b4806a7cb7a79bc75","tid":827631,"uid":1654,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T05:45:45.000Z","msg":"示範一次等佢模仿"},{"pid":"0e0c3d9e6667b4d810c997789c27949f8a7bd619","tid":827631,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T05:57:29.000Z","msg":"拎塊尿布放去你想佢去既地方<br />\n之後不停迫佢嗅"},{"pid":"d266e4ad1970671a3068638db264463b43e9befb","tid":827631,"uid":188637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T07:48:52.000Z","msg":"應該由細教架...<br />\n不過大約係知佢幾時屙就捉佢去嗰到, 等佢屙.. (大約係嗅嗅下, 轉下圈.)<br />\n屙咗唔啱地方, 用尿布吸少少, 話下佢, 帶佢去你想佢屙嗰到, 話佢知, 屙錯嗰到用滴露拖一拖, 搞到無味. <br />\n重複2 星期左右.. <br />\n困係無用的, 困佢係你想佢屙嗰到, 反而搞到佢唔敢去嗰到.."},{"pid":"c7616664e6ee4a308a7041a6768eaef4071d028c","tid":827631,"uid":190526,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T09:15:56.000Z","msg":"成屋鋪曬尿布 佢痾起邊都唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495951a7fb1e09c104aa6c7e80ff53d1c6510d27","tid":827631,"uid":43966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T22:50:28.000Z","msg":"同你問題一樣唉 我隻狗4個月大"},{"pid":"1af96965b1921f5de79dce0c2b0520c94337f4c3","tid":827631,"uid":44031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T23:02:48.000Z","msg":"1歲應該教唔到了"},{"pid":"100c2ef3ccece4242ee8bd8281dd1e5ecd240946","tid":827631,"uid":88914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:42:18.000Z","msg":"因為我係近來先養佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以都好煩惱呀"},{"pid":"69bccdc471a868e9158d2c4f340d0180d0728842","tid":827631,"uid":88914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"495951a7fb1e09c104aa6c7e80ff53d1c6510d27","tid":827631,"uid":43966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T22:50:28.000Z","msg":"同你問題一樣唉 我隻狗4個月大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:42:40.000Z","msg":"4個月大應該都易教少少"},{"pid":"6a78cfefeaa2ea2bcdf8cb73343c36b83390c5ec","tid":827631,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:56:02.000Z","msg":"都係屙岩地方就好誇張咁讚<br />\n但屙錯千祁唔好鬧<br />\n會嚇到佢唔敢屙"},{"pid":"177ffaa461b172215b340835342399b17dc95d9f","tid":827631,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1af96965b1921f5de79dce0c2b0520c94337f4c3","tid":827631,"uid":44031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T23:02:48.000Z","msg":"1歲應該教唔到了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:56:24.000Z","msg":"肯教一定教到"},{"pid":"72c8e64034e3951272f454bd8557e3137f5a8259","tid":827631,"uid":205222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T04:00:23.000Z","msg":"擺d佢既小便或大便係你想佢去廁所既位置<br />\n之後佢都會去返果度柯<br />\n柯岩位就比零食佢做獎勵<br />\n狗狗會認定一個位上大小二便<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0eb2af393969c20a3b03d6e6eaca6cc73b15db","tid":827631,"uid":532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"177ffaa461b172215b340835342399b17dc95d9f","tid":827631,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1af96965b1921f5de79dce0c2b0520c94337f4c3","tid":827631,"uid":44031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T23:02:48.000Z","msg":"1歲應該教唔到了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:56:24.000Z","msg":"肯教一定教到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:56:42.000Z","msg":"我個隻12歲都未識去廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14cbddd4250058bc26da05a20c0a3ccd08e9a79c","tid":827631,"uid":14052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T18:28:34.000Z","msg":"我果時開頭係要監察住佢<br />\n佢一柯就抱佢入去佢個廁所<br />\n柯岩就有零食仔 <br />\n之後就識柯了<br />\n不過後尾間唔時都會賴（一兩日賴一次）<br />\n唔知佢做乜鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b368d405944b6f5347c70c894302451c3f2c59","tid":827631,"uid":13313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T22:51:34.000Z","msg":"1. 尿布上沾上佢d尿味，之後佢行過聞到就知果度係屙尿既地方<br />\n2. 佢屙錯位要即刻清 清潔到完全冇味<br />\n3. 屙岩位要即刻獎零食<br />\n <br />\n我隻狗個零月就學識 但一開始都會零零星星屙錯位 成為左習慣就唔會錯了"},{"pid":"716ee3e5c0a3027fef6e4328241511043d30a113","tid":827631,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T23:11:11.000Z","msg":"得一隻狗好易教<br />\n買 定點去廁所 引導劑<br />\n又或者拎張尿墊 沾啲佢尿味 擺係你想佢去屙嘅位<br />\n佢去之前會周圍聞 <br />\n聞到就會去<br />\n<br />\n最好就奄咗佢<br />\n咪會周圍屙 霸地盤"},{"pid":"7425a716c7870a4739ed2e81037d1de0ba5e969e","tid":827631,"uid":1367,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T23:43:06.000Z","msg":"打到佢飛起la 𨳒"},{"pid":"cb017590ca211863fa5617662f565e949d1904e3","tid":827631,"uid":42879,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T00:14:15.000Z","msg":"我本身隻狗就一拎返黎係龍養左一兩日，之後拆個底出黎做廁所，每次去完都比小小獎佢，去錯地方就拎尿布抺返佢放返廁所，要比佢睇住，捉佢去聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前有朋友去旅行，放低左另一隻狗，一開始痾出面又係拎片尿布去索左先，再去返廁所比佢聞，睇住佢一次就識之後去廁所痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲醒到一次屎分幾次痾呃零食<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8726d60b73de1eb6e196c5a1b465feeb411047a5","tid":827631,"uid":43966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T16:43:42.000Z","msg":"點解我隻狗咁多屎屙？一日屙5次<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  bb貴婦黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5f23d2ecd2c1e50a2b9d190ea4550663159c91","tid":827631,"uid":72735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:05:57.000Z","msg":"我隻領養返黎三歲<br />\n好辛苦先教到一半<br />\n佢會識係盤屙，個有時會出界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋如果已經係盤度屙左尿就唔肯同一個位屙屎，會係隔離地板屙<br />\n所以次次出街返黎地下通常都有屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最慘係佢唔中意食野，正餐都唔係點食<br />\n好難獎勵佢幫助訓練"},{"pid":"e6036616fac3da51005c3a88093e431ffed3a626","tid":827631,"uid":88914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T11:18:01.000Z","msg":"唔知有無人仲有睇 不過好開心地呢2日成功左啦算<br />\n佢會自己去個廁所屙屎了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 送上屎圖一幅<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/191736_3947df6bc02efe585ac13b5dd58dc40d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F191736_3947df6bc02efe585ac13b5dd58dc40d.png&h=dd7a4d38&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n好有成功感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f39e39dad38e86775194a155a718cacd876eda","tid":827631,"uid":45428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6036616fac3da51005c3a88093e431ffed3a626","tid":827631,"uid":88914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T11:18:01.000Z","msg":"唔知有無人仲有睇 不過好開心地呢2日成功左啦算<br />\n佢會自己去個廁所屙屎了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 送上屎圖一幅<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/191736_3947df6bc02efe585ac13b5dd58dc40d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F191736_3947df6bc02efe585ac13b5dd58dc40d.png&h=dd7a4d38&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n好有成功感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:18:49.000Z","msg":"好好呀 叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8940c5315bd8d059f96b08884760b470ddededa4","tid":827631,"uid":173456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T04:57:40.000Z","msg":"我屋企隻貴婦教到佢6歲都就黎都唔識去廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b5d558ee74c56c4d2695b00f1dbc441fb8bf68","tid":827631,"uid":138023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:01:17.000Z","msg":"我果隻唔洗教無端端識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd7aa60b7446063072f73b6cf789cd1f0065727","tid":827631,"uid":29249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T14:41:17.000Z","msg":"我就係用索尿放去想佢去嘅地方 教左成個月都未識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求賜教"}]}